 1991-18591991-09-260PWC,  ,  ,  , 
PrecisAuthority for the NATIONAL CAPITAL COMMISSION to sell a number of its real property holdings situated in Ottawa, Ontario, all located in those parts of town known as the Ottawa Business Park and the Hawthorne Business Park, as follows: (a) some 1.4 hectares located at 3145 Conroy Road to the REGIONAL MUNICIPALITY OF OTTAWA-CARLETON, and (b) two pieces of land located at 2464 Russell Road to the CORPORATION OF THE CITY OF OTTAWA, which together contain an area of some 23.4 hectares.
